                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"><a href="http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Guides&message.id=10#M10" target="_blank">http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Guides&message.id=10Num.M10</a>
